  "body": "<h1>PataLand3</h1>\n<strong>If you have any questions or suggestions, do not hesitate to contact us in our Discord.</strong>\n<h2>What's PataLand3</h2>\n<p>PataLand3 is a Modpack for the PataLand3 server. As its name suggests, it is the third edition. This Modpack is made to work on the server side and on the client side. It is a perfect adventure pack for multiplayer. This ModPack is made with requests from server participants. It is a very complete ModPack and includes all kinds of things. With this ModPack you will have a lot of fun for a long time.</p>\n<p>This ModPack has a lot of animals thanks to \"Alex's mobs\" and thanks to \"Beyond Earth\" you can travel to planets with very good mechanics. And with its own mod, it's the perfect ModPack for the server PataLand3.</p>\n<h2>Why play PataLand3</h2>\n<p>PataLand ModPack has lots of different types of mods to do your experience more fun, it has lots of mechanics and you can do lots of things with it. In one player or multiplayer mode, it's the best option.\n<h2>List of resources used</h2>\n<details close>\n<summary>\nMods\n</summary>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/skin-layers-3d\">3D Skin Layers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/alexs-mobs\">Alex's Mobs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ambientsounds\">Ambient Sounds 5</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/another-furniture\">Another Furniture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/appleskin\">AppleSkin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/artifacts\">Artifacts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/beyond-earth\">Beyond Earth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/chat-heads\">Chat Heads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/citadel\">Citadel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/comforts\">Comforts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/configured\">Configured</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/corpse\">Corpse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cosmetic-armor-reworked\">CosmeticArmorReworked</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create\">Create</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/creativecore\">CreativeCore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/creatures-and-beasts\">Creatures and Beasts</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/creeper-overhaul\">Creeper Overhaul</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/curios\">Curios API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/diagonal-fences\">Diagonal Fences</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/drippy-loading-screen\">Drippy Loading Screen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dynamic-lights\">Dynamic Lights</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/openblocks-elevator\">Open Blocks Elevator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/emojiful\">Emojiful</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/emotecraft-forge\">Emotecraft</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/expandability\">ExpandAbility</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/falling-tree\">FallingTree</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fancymenu-forge\">FancyMenu</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/flashs-npcs\">Flash's NPCs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib\">Geckolib</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immersive-paintings\">Immersive Paintings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/inventory-hud-forge\">Inventory HUD+</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jade\">Jade</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jei\">Just Enough Items</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-enough-professions-jep\">Just Enough Professions (JEP)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-enough-resources-jer\">Just Enough Resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/konkrete\">Koncrete</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/minetraps\">MineTraps</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/more-crafting-tables-mct\">More Crafting Tables Mod</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/more-player-models\">More Player Models</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mrcrayfish-furniture-mod\">MrCrayfish's Furniture Mod</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/oculus\">Oculus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/oh-the-biomes-youll-go\">Oh The Biomes You'll Go</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pams-harvestcraft-2-crops\">Pam's Harvestcraft 2 - Crops</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pams-harvestcraft-2-food-core\">Pam's Harvestcraft 2 - Food Core</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pams-harvestcraft-2-food-extended\">Pam's Harvestcraft 2 - Food Extended</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pams-harvestcraft-2-trees\">Pam's Harvestcraft 2 - Trees</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/pataland3-mod\">PataLand3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/playeranimator\">Player Anim